{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require companies to provide a simple method of cancelling online subscriptions",
        "additional_details": "Citizens should not be forced to jump through hoops and dodge confusing design patterns to cancel a subscription that was set up quickly and easily.\r\n\r\nI want the government to ban companies from:\r\n* Making cancellation process hard to find\r\n* Encouraging users to accidentally exit the process\r\n* Forcing users to make phone calls\r\n\r\nI think that this is all designed to trap customers into keeping services they don't want.",
        "background": "I want the government to require companies to provide a simple method of cancelling online subscriptions. As an ADHD sufferer, I suffer from poor impulse control and a short attention span.",
